{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/1.gif?t=1628498556\" /><br><br>High school student Kihara Kashin is trapped by an unknown force in Kuromori-ch\u014d. She accidentally ran into Kiritani Yuki who told her she had to travel to the past in order to get out of Kuromori-ch\u014d.<br><br>And so, the adventure begins.<br>What lies ahead, is not just the secrets hidden behind Kuromori-ch\u014d,<br>but the strange and exciting world of y\u014dkai.<br><br><strong>Feature</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/2.gif?t=1628498556\" /><br><br>\u00b7The main story has three immersive chapters.<br>\u00b7The story is based on historical events mixed with our own imagination to provide an unusual and attractive narrative. <br>\u00b7Simple and descriptive narration and dialogue. The game also provides a thrilling adventure.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/3.gif?t=1628498556\" /><br><br>\u00b7You will meet a diverse cast of characters along your journey, and you will never feel alone in Tales of the Black Forest. <br>\u00b7On a side note, there will be LOTS of cats!!!!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/4.gif?t=1628498556\" /><br><br>\u00b7Unique Japanese setting with a pixel anime style that will please your eyes.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/5.gif?t=1628498556\" /><br><br>\u00b7Puzzles at the right difficulty and thought-provoking riddles to provide you with such a smooth ride you\u2019ll never get bored in this world.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/6.gif?t=1628498556\" /><br><br>\u00b7With so many Easter Eggs and bonuses scattered around Kuromori-ch\u014d, we invite you to discover them all! They might just make your day.<br><br>English subtitles proofread by woosk from Visual novel, JRPG, Anime and partner website Sinical Network.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Girl under the Moonlight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/ca8baf9851d69379986b9385a89d810e7606d40d.jpg"},{"name":"Bone Mountain and Blossoms","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/6a29dc12d74ec2f82ba797b9b183f9f7445db820.jpg"},{"name":"Cluck cluck cluck?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/b4eb1e4760c2b6a73b3127b1dc14e90df03f839d.jpg"},{"name":"Don\u2019t fool the scarecrow","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/4dde8beb4355fad008a3e33424a49883ee241ec3.jpg"},{"name":"The imprisoned Snowcat","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/458dae139cdffc72876d025ec20298d35d52ea75.jpg"},{"name":"The lost kitten has returned to the fairy tale kingdom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/e2c243ff22eba5963b25de487afa790de31aa8e1.jpg"},{"name":"The black cat's true face","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/2878c79748d7c5eb54c736050d8d03209fc544f9.jpg"},{"name":"Repairman, tourist, chef","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/7a6244e2390a9ec71651be38c02bb7dd01204988.jpg"},{"name":"A god's ceremony","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/0d887c04dec0bb4f4b54c1e90cda34553f53e6dc.jpg"},{"name":"Comedy and Tragedy, Love and Be Loved","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1093910/70d436de8deb3705ecdda397b752